:"https://github.com/timdorr","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timdorr/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timdorr/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timdorr/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timdorr/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timdorr/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timdorr/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timdorr/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timdorr/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/timdorr/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/remix-run/react-router/issues/comments/723241746","html_url":"https://github.com/remix-run/react-router/issues/7598#issuecomment-723241746","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/remix-run/react-router/issues/7598","id":723241746,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDcyMzI0MTc0Ng==","user":{"login":"hugmanrique","id":6255580,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYyNTU1ODA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6255580?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique","html_url":"https://github.com/hugmanrique","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-11-06T18:49:05Z","updated_at":"2020-11-07T12:39:57Z","body":"I agree that adding that boilerplate to every custom `Link` implementation isn't a clean solution. However, while inspecting https://github.com/ReactTraining/react-router/blob/dev-experimental/packages/react-router-dom/index.tsx#L235 I noticed the `handleClick` function. Is passing that function as the `onClick` handler to the built component from `component`/`as` an option? I think that would hide the implementation details (the `CustomLink` doesn't know what the `onClick` function does, only ensures it's passed to the final DOM rendered component). This approach doesn't require passing the `navigate` prop (which may be a downside to some? if so, how?). My rationale is that a `CustomLink` passed as the `component` prop to a `Link` should only modify its aesthetics, not its behavior.","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/remix-run/react-router/issues/comments/723241746/reactions","total_count":3,"+1":3,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"hugmanrique","id":6255580,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYyNTU1ODA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6255580?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique","html_url":"https://github.com/hugmanrique","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hugmanrique/events{/priv